elping this young person and it was like something to exult in . The script could have been written by Planned Parenthood.<br /><br />All in all , this is a cheap show that lacks much of a future unless it decides to present more real relationships rather than just totally unbelievable soap opera relationships and far - fetched medical situations throughout the whole show .
