 a disappointment . Oh , and as for the reason every person actually watched this film , Shahrukh Khan made a good debut . He excelled in the very little his part allowed him to do . The late Divya Bharti made a promising debut as well . If you want to watch this film , go for the second half only . Personally , I would not do even that .
